{"ts": "2026-06-08T04:20:26.156145+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Findings\n\n### 1. Package Manager\n\nThe repository expects contributors to use **npm**. The `CONTRIBUTING.md` explicitly states:\n\n> *\"Maintainer note: we standardize on npm for contributor setup now, so ignore any yarn-oriented scripts or labels that still appear in package metadata during migration.\"*\n\nAlthough a `yarn.lock` file and some `yarn` references still exist in `package.json` scripts (e.g., `\"fix\": \"yarn lint --fix\"`) and `Taskfile.yaml` (e.g., `yarn install`, `yarn release`), these are legacy artefacts from an ongoing migration. The official policy for contributors is **npm**.\n\n---\n\n### 2. Environment-Specific Script Names\n\n#### From `package.json` (npm scripts)\n\n| Script | Purpose | Environment |\n|--------|---------|-------------|\n| `dev` | Start dev server (local) | `NODE_ENV=local` |\n| `dev:stg` | Start dev server (staging) | `NODE_ENV=stg` |\n| `serve` | Preview the built app | — |\n| `build` | Build for prod mode | `--mode prod` |\n| `build:stg` | Build for test/staging | `--mode test` |\n| `build:prod` | Build for production | `--mode production` |\n| `deploy` | Deploy `dist/` to GitHub Pages | — |\n| `lint` | Lint source files (ESLint) | — |\n| `fix` | Auto-fix lint issues | — |\n\n#### From `Taskfile.yaml` (go-task tasks)\n\n| Task | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `init` | Initialise the project (install global npm tools, copy `.env.local`, run `yarn install`) |\n| `changelog` | Generate `CHANGELOG.md` |\n| `release` | Run the release workflow (`yarn release` + changelog + commit) |\n| `commit` | Stage, commit with Commitizen, and push |\n\n#### Environment Variable Files (`envs/`)\n\n| File | Environment | Key details |\n|------|-------------|-------------|\n| `.env.local` | Local development | `VITE_BUILD_ENV=development`, mock API |\n| `.env.stg` | Staging | `VITE_BUILD_ENV=production`, staging API |\n| `.env.prod` | Production | `VITE_BUILD_ENV=production`, production API |\n\nThe `init` task in `Taskfile.yaml` copies `envs/.env.local` → `.env` as the default environment for contributors getting started.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 940, "prompt_tokens": 11012, "total_tokens": 11952, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 373, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 10624}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 10624, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 388}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "53de96e7-615f-4964-830c-f22eaa9cc91b", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea575-aef2-7b93-972d-cb63918488d4-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11012, "output_tokens": 940, "total_tokens": 11952, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 10624}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 373}}}}]}}}
